🚀 Features
Location Lookup: Identifies the country or region associated with a phone number.
Carrier Info: Retrieves the name of the service provider (e.g., Airtel, Jio, Verizon).
Geocoding: Converts location descriptions into precise latitude and longitude coordinates.
Map Visualization: Generates a professional interactive map (.html) with a marker at the identified location. 
.

📂 Project Structure
main.py: Your primary script containing the logic.
myphone.py: A helper file containing the variable number (the phone number you want to track).
mylocation.html: The interactive map file generated after running the script. 
