📖 How to Use
Prepare your data: In myphone.py, add your target number in E.164 format (e.g., +14155552671).
Update API Key: Replace the key variable in the script with your own OpenCage API Key.

⚠️ Important Note
This script provides the approximate location based on the phone number's registered region or country. It cannot track a mobile phone's real-time physical movement or pinpoint an exact street address due to privacy and technical limitations of public libraries.
